name: 2022 Collectors' Edition by A Big Blue Bird

metadata.name: Relive #1/16
metadata.description:
These edition of 16 pieces is a thank you Christmas gift to my amazing collectors! Thank you for your incredible support and being a part of my wonderful journey in the NFT space.

Words do little justice in fully conveying my gratitude and I hope that you will enjoy this little token of my appreciation which is very much a part of myself.

15 of these editions will go out to collectors of my minted pieces as of Christmas Eve 2022, with the 16th piece remaining in my collection.
